    designPreferences: ["Respectful restoration of original architectural elements – wooden beams, jharokhas, courtyards", "Modern comforts seamlessly integrated into traditional spaces", "Warm earth tones complementing natural materials", "Garden integration as central design element", "Library and study spaces reflecting intellectual character", "Vintage furniture restoration honoring heritage", "Contemporary kitchens and bathrooms hidden from living areas", "Courtyard designs maintaining traditional ventilation and light", "Blending old and new materials thoughtfully"],
